---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="ToolVader – Free Business Tools for Freelancers & Solopreneurs"
  description="Free online tools for freelancers, consultants and solopreneurs. Calculate freelance rates, generate project quotes and manage your business with ToolVader."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-12 pt-10 sm:pb-16 lg:flex lg:px-8 lg:pt-32">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl flex-shrink-0 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-xl lg:pt-8">
        <h1 class="mt-10 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
          Free Business Tools for Freelancers & Solopreneurs
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
          Set the right price for your expertise. Our free online business tools and calculators help freelancers, consultants, and solopreneurs make data-driven decisions to grow their business.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-6">
          <a href="/tools/freelance-rate-calculator" class="rounded-md bg-gray-900 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-gray-900 transition-colors">
            Open Freelance Rate Calculator
          </a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">
            Learn More <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Featured Tools Section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50/50 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">Featured Tool</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Freelance Rate Calculator Card -->
          <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Freelance Rate Calculator</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                Determine what you should charge clients based on profession, experience, location, and business expenses.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
              <a href="/tools/freelance-rate-calculator" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">
                Launch Calculator <span aria-hidden="true" class="ml-2">→</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Project Price Calculator Card -->
          <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Project Price Calculator</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
                Convert your hourly rate into professional fixed-price project quotes. Factor in complexity and revision rounds.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
              <a href="/tools/project-price-calculator" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">
                Launch Calculator <span aria-hidden="true" class="ml-2">→</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Why Choose ToolVader Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Why Freelancers Choose ToolVader</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
          In today's fast-paced independent economy, making informed financial decisions is the difference between a struggling side-hustle and a thriving professional practice. ToolVader provides the essential utilities that independent professionals need to navigate the complexities of modern business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-12 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p>
            For <strong>freelance designers and developers</strong>, our calculators take the guesswork out of pricing. By factoring in specific market demand, regional multipliers, and individual business expenses, you can ensure that every quote you send is both competitive and sustainable. No more undercharging or losing projects to vague pricing strategies.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-8">
            <strong>Consultants and strategists</strong> use ToolVader to translate their deep expertise into clear, value-based rates. Whether you are advising an enterprise client or a small startup, our tools help you justify your fees with data-driven logic, allowing you to focus on delivering high-impact results for your clients.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>
            <strong>Solopreneurs and creative writers</strong> often face the challenge of managing diverse income streams while tracking overhead costs. Our platform simplifies these financial hurdles, providing a centralized place to project monthly revenue and understand your true profitability. We empower you to manage your business with the same precision as a large agency.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-8">
            At ToolVader, we are committed to supporting the global community of marketers, engineers, and independent creators. Our mission is to provide professional-grade business utilities that remain accessible, free, and privacy-focused, ensuring you have the tools to build your legacy on your own terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
